snippet.textDisplay:
Many girls nd guys r saying that this song has some parts of punjabi...
Thing is that punjabi(central punjab), siraiki(south punjab), pothwari(Rawalpindi,islamabad), hindko(hazara division) r all same kind of languages nd have mostly same words being used....
A person speaking any one of these languages can easily understand and talk to people of other languages mentioned above....
Like i speak hindko but can easily understand nd even speak pujabi, pothwari nd a bit of siraiki...
